title: MP3 Music from Yo Gabba Gabba!
description:
Music ripped from DIVX copies of the first Season of Yo Gabba Gabba!

Yo Gabba Gabba! is a Children&#039;s television series airing on Nick Jr. created by Christian Jacobs (alias The MC Bat Commander) and Scott Schultz. 

A top rated hit with kids and child like adults, Yo Gabba Gabba! is hosted by DJ Lance Rock, and five toy monsters: Brobee, Foofa, Muno, Plex, and Toodee. 

Trippy images, music and nostalgic 80&#039;s video games fill the world of Yo Gabba Gabba as pre-schoolers learn of love, respect and the world around them.

Songs include, I&#039;m So Happy & Be Kind to Animals by The Salteens, Pool Party and Share by The Aquabats, Pajama Party Time by Smoosh, Banana by the Aggrolites. See file list for all 20 ripped songs. (35:44 total time)
